org.nd4j.nativeblas

Class Nd4jCpu.OpRegistrator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.bytedeco.javacpp.Pointer
      • org.nd4j.nativeblas.Nd4jCpu.OpRegistrator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AutoCloseable
    Enclosing class:
    Nd4jCpu

    @Namespace(value="nd4j::ops")
 @NoOffset
public static class Nd4jCpu.OpRegistrator
extends org.bytedeco.javacpp.Pointer
    This class provides runtime ops lookup, based on opName or opHash. To build lookup directory we use *_OP_IMPL macro, which puts static structs at compile time in .cpp files, so once binary is executed, static objects are initialized automatically, and we get list of all ops available at runtime via this singleton.
